    {"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Cultural Context"}],"depth":2,"type":"heading"},
    {"children":[{"type":"text","value":"适合 reflects Chinese values of harmony and natural compatibility. Finding what is 适合 is\nconsidered wisdom, as it avoids conflict and promotes success. Chinese culture emphasizes the\nimportance of matching people to appropriate roles and situations, believing that harmony comes from\nnatural compatibility rather than forcing incompatible elements together."}],"type":"paragraph"}
